    - Placeholder [[#1234](https://github.com/phw198/OutlookGoogleCalendarSync/issues/2321)]
- Sync Engine
    - Placeholder [[#1234](https://github.com/phw198/OutlookGoogleCalendarSync/issues/2321)]

&lt;i class="em em-beetle"&gt;&lt;/i&gt; **Bugfix**  

- Application
    - Placeholder [[#1234](https://github.com/phw198/OutlookGoogleCalendarSync/issues/2321)]

- Sync Engine
    - Logging Google exception without start date prevents sync [[#2321](https://github.com/phw198/OutlookGoogleCalendarSync/issues/2321)]
    </releaseNotes>
